snippet.title: Sifu - Vengeance Edition Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/sifu/

Check out the retail VENGEANCE special edition of SIFU, available in stores starting from May 3, 2022.
Exclusive items and content will include an official Steelbook®, a print artbook, and 3 lithographs.
Pre-orders are open.
